Everyone in position? Eye in the sky.
Gee, gotta work on those rhymes!
It's Luna that's gotta work on stuff.
Like learning that crime doesn't pay.
I'm having a moon tea party. They're perfect.
But I was just getting started!
And my surprise guest is here.
Too bad you're not invited, Bird Brain. [laughs]
You take Motsuki and the moths. I've got Luna.
Ha! How about I be the teacher tonight?
See ya next lesson, Feathers. I'm off to the…
Maybe we… call it a night?
Ha, ha! That clumsy bird won't be bothering us anymore tonight.
-Now, that's what I call a tea party! -[giggles]
You've stopped us spinning into outer space.
What could make you fly better than that?
Uh… and um, getting those teacups back, of course.
Catboy, take the controls and go distract Luna!
Tsk, tsk, PJ Masks. This is my party.
Do they really think I'd invite a mangy cat,
How's that for a flying move?
Uh, at least we got the teacups?
Come on! Let's get that tea set back where it belongs.
We go to fortress? Party games?
-Great job last night. -You were, like, vroom.
And they were, like, "Oh, no!" And you were, like, swoosh.
-And Luna was "Why me?" -But we didn't get back at her.
She's just so mean to me sometimes.
Luna's not bad all the time.
When's she's good, she's pretty good.
And when she's bad, she's awful.
Come on. You have to rise above it.
-That's what being a hero is about. -[school bell rings]
someone's not being so nice to me.
They're all nice. They're in our class.
This girl doesn't even go to our school.
Play with us. We'll have fun.
Amaya's sure got the Luna Blues.
You know, when we do the thing we do at night,
and we meet "a certain person", who likes the Moon…
Still don't know what you're talking about.
But I think Amaya's pretty upset with Luna.
A few nights with no Moon, no magnet, no fortress, no…
Not just her! The Moon's under attack!
Come on. It's what we do.
Save the day, no matter what.
Not even Luna's gonna stop me doing that.
PJ Masks, we're on our way…
[all] Into the night to save the day!
And a brave band of heroes
is ready to face fiendish villains to stop them messing with your day!
Motsuki and Luna need help. Eeep!
Romeo's robots are blasting all over the place trying to get in.
Imagine what Romeo could do with moon crystals.
Romeo's flown his factory almost into space.
He must be controlling his Moon attack from there.
We've got to stop him. Hang in there, Luna!
Another wave of Flybots to the Moon.
if they don't receive my genius instructions.
We are attacking the Luna Fortress.
But the Moon Girl shoots rays at us.
are examining the Luna wand force field.
Soon I will discover its weakest spot.
Change of plan, Robot. I want you here.
Remember what we're going to do when I get them?
But only after I've carried out my awesomely evil plan.
Romeo's sending instructions with those transmitters.
Lead them away in the glider. I'll fly solo.
I should get close enough to use my Super Owl feathers.
-[Luna] What's the hold up? -Don't worry, Owlette's on it!
Come on! We don't have much time!
Uh-uh, I'm not letting her mess this up.
Keep the force field up. Now get me there.
Either that or leave things to cuckoo girl.
Only because she sent me spinning!
Oh no, I'm taking it from here.
Get ready for good news, Flybots!
And now, Motsuki? What else are you gonna mess up?
Don't blame me! You should've… Whoa!
No victory dancing until my plan is all done.
Bad is beautiful, my robot friend.
The end of the PJ Masks!
You kept getting in my way.
Motsuki's a teeny little moth again!
I had a clear shot until you stuck your big head in.
Who are you calling big head?
Uh, perhaps we should all go inside and have a glass of milk?
No more arguing. We'll get the crystals back.
Let's chase Romeo with everything we've got.
If you want to make up for losing my crystals!
You're the one who should be making up for stuff.
Oh, I think so. Don't you?
Not now that we've got this!
The PJ Crystal! It's got all our powers!
Hey, my moon crystals are pretty good too.
I know! He wanted them all!
And now he's got them, who knows what he's going to do.
Well, I am an excellent pilot.
Ha! We'll fix that! I have what we need.
Ready to be used in my most villainous plan ever.
Why can't you be like the good little moon crystals?
I'll take your power, you'll see!
I shouldn't have let you get to me.
Yeah, that's what she said. Kinda strange, huh?
I'll get all the crystals back!
Don't let the Flying Factory out of your sight!
We'll think of something. We're PJ Masks.
What's happening to my Cat Car?
It must be because of the crystal.
I thought I had it bad.
At least I've still got you mothies.
Got to find Catboy and Gekko. It's not too late.
If I can't take your power all at once,
I'll take it bit by bit.
It's the middle of the night.
This is a cat-tastrophe! What are we gonna do?
Wait? She's calling it a night?
